00:16:28,955 --> 00:16:31,645
Yeah, that was awesome
how you saved his life and all.

266
00:16:32,191 --> 00:16:35,381
That was just unbelievable. Really.

267
00:16:37,697 --> 00:16:39,917
You here for the surf contest?

268
