271
00:16:49,642 --> 00:16:51,512
-That's your job.
-Are you gonna kiss her?

272
00:16:51,944 --> 00:16:53,723
-What's going on?
-Come on, Joe.

273
00:16:54,146 --> 00:16:56,136
-You were saying you were in love--
-No, I didn't say that.

274
00:16:56,582 --> 00:16:58,072
-Look, he really digs you.
-Joe, listen--

275
00:16:58,451 --> 00:17:00,351
