Stop! What are you doing?

303
00:18:40,853 --> 00:18:42,723
Look, everybody, it's Big Z's last fan!

304
00:18:43,189 --> 00:18:44,829
Coming through.
Out of the way. Let's go.

305
00:18:45,224 --> 00:18:46,974
-You don't deserve to talk about him.
-He's a big zero.

306
00:18:47,393 --> 00:18:48,703
-Shut your mouth!
-Zero starts with "Z"!

307
00:18:49,061 --> 00:18:51,551
You'll never be
as good as Big Z, Stank.

308
00:18:53,032 --> 00:18:56,162
Hey, hey, people, come on now.
Smile on your brother.

309
00:18:56,769 --> 00:19:00,579
