with your head.

324
00:20:20,753 --> 00:20:23,622
-Bring it on, pecker face. Let's go.
-Pecker face?

325
00:20:28,294 --> 00:20:29,464
It's mine!

326
00:20:39,705 --> 00:20:41,405
So, Cody, when you take
your first wave...

327
00:20:41,807 --> 00:20:43,977
..and the whole island's there
to watch, what'll it be like?

328
00:20:44,443 --> 00:20:46,933
It's gonna be amazing.
It'll be the best wave of my life.

329
00:20:47,446 --> 00:20:49,555
I hope the cameras are rolling
because you'll want to watch it...

330
00:20:50,015 --> 00:20:53,115
..over and over and over again.
It's gonna be awesome!

331
00:21:08,601 --> 00:21:09,831
I can't look.

332
00:21:10,503 --> 00:21:13,663
-Poor kid. He's-- Poor kid.
-Wow! That was spectacular!

333
00:21:17,309 --> 00:21:19,559
I'm number one! The Tank!

334
00:21:54,313 --> 00:21:57,353
We're trying to get the details.
The lifeguard just pulled him in.

335
00:22:01,287 --> 00:22:04,327
That's what happens
when you take on the Tank, right?

336
00:22:06,559 --> 00:22:07,609
Cody, Cody!

337
00:22:07,927 --> 00:22:10,266
-How is he? Okay? What can I do?
-Yeah, he's okay.

338
00:22:10,763 --> 00:22:15,153
I can help. Except if there's blood.
Just the thought of blood makes me....

339
00:22:16,569 --> 00:22:18,349
Somebody help the chicken.

340
00:22:18,771 --> 00:22:20,961
-Tank, you okay?
-Tank needs fuel.

341
00:22:21,774 --> 00:22:23,704
Mikey, get the board, will you?

342
00:22:24,476 --> 00:22:26,346
Come on. Come on. Come on.

343
00:22:30,950 --> 00:22:35,460
-Did I win? I won, huh?
-You should've stayed in Antarctica.

344
00:22:37,089 --> 00:22:38,899
-Oh, wow.
-You're gonna be okay.

345
00:22:39,325 --> 00:22:43,015
Look at that.
There's pixies everywhere.

346
00:22:44,997 --> 00:22:48,067
What do you think about Cody going
into a contest and possibly winning?

347
00:22:48,667 --> 00:22:49,567
-You know, I'm--
-Ha.

348
00:22:49,869 --> 00:22:53,178
-Why did you just laugh?
-Because he keeps saying "possible."

349
00:22:53,806 --> 00:22:57,706
Like it's "possible" that you're gonna
win. And you're gonna do anything.

350
00:22:58,410 --> 00:23:01,370
-Really, what are the chances?
-They're high. Aren't they high?

351
00:23:02,081 --> 00:23:05,650
