It's not like I'm, like, the underdog.

352
00:23:16,762 --> 00:23:20,922
Hey, Geek! Geek!
Get up and help me.

353
00:23:21,800 --> 00:23:23,090
Geek.

354
00:23:24,036 --> 00:23:25,406
Geek?

355
00:23:27,473 --> 00:23:31,163
Geek. Wake up! I need your help.

356
00:23:32,177 --> 00:23:34,197
Come on. Get off your lazy butt
and come and help me.

357
00:23:34,647 --> 00:23:36,107
--beautiful dream.

358
00:23:36,482 --> 00:23:39,382
-Did you ever know Sheila?
-No. I don't know Sheila.

359
00:23:39,952 --> 00:23:41,682
-Wait, wait, wait. What?
-What?

360
00:23:42,087 --> 00:23:42,956
Who's this guy?

361
00:23:43,255 --> 00:23:45,655
-He's a surfer. He's hurt.
-Who are all those guys?

362
00:23:46,158 --> 00:23:48,027
