363
00:23:48,460 --> 00:23:49,980
-Come on.
-Lani, what are you doing?

364
00:23:50,362 --> 00:23:52,262
If you help him, they'll go away.

365
00:23:52,698 --> 00:23:54,918
-Hey! Get out of here!
-Help him!

366
00:23:56,035 --> 00:23:58,405
-Where do you want him?
-Nowhere. That's the whole point.

367
00:23:58,904 --> 00:24:01,564
-No outsiders. Come on.
-I know, I know, I know.

368
00:24:02,107 --> 00:24:05,917
This is an emergency. He went down
bad over the falls. 1 don't know if he--

369
00:24:09,748 --> 00:24:11,388
