-I don't know.

370
00:24:11,784 --> 00:24:13,094
I'm not sure. I got him after--

371
00:24:13,452 --> 00:24:15,032
-What, is he your boyfriend?
-No. No.

372
00:24:15,421 --> 00:24:18,551
Wait, wait, wait.
Looks like he stepped on a fire urchin.

373
00:24:19,825 --> 00:24:22,895
Stepped on me? Are you kidding?
This guy was dancing on me.

374
00:24:24,663 --> 00:24:28,003
Just look at this. Broken, broken,
gone, gone, broken, broken, broken....

375
00:24:28,634 --> 00:24:32,884
This is pretty bad.
This is really bad.

376
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:36,120
-What-- Cody!
-I hurt.

377
00:24:36,508 --> 00:24:39,498
