pushing the poison all over his body.

383
00:24:57,997 --> 00:24:59,957
-Come on, come on.
-l know he looks--

384
00:25:00,866 --> 00:25:02,156
Here it is.

385
00:25:03,402 --> 00:25:05,152
-What are you doing?
-What is he doing?

386
00:25:05,571 --> 00:25:06,711
This is a sure-fire cure.

387
00:25:07,039 --> 00:25:10,519
I learned it from an old medicine
man. It, well, works wonders.

388
00:25:11,210 --> 00:25:13,020
-What? No! Not that!
-Not what?

389
00:25:13,479 --> 00:25:15,409
What is he gonna-- Gonna what?

390
00:25:16,315 --> 00:25:17,605
-Come on, now.
-Geek, stop.

391
00:25:17,950 --> 00:25:20,970
