some water sounds?

392
00:25:21,553 --> 00:25:23,573
-Oh, my gosh, this is so gross.
-What is water sounds?

393
00:25:24,023 --> 00:25:27,303
-Come on. Here we go.
-No, no, no. You--

394
00:25:31,730 --> 00:25:34,420
Kid, you better keep your mouth shut.
See, what'd I tell you?

395
00:25:34,967 --> 00:25:37,657
Hold his foot still, Lani. Come on.
Knock him out or something.

396
00:25:38,203 --> 00:25:40,103
-I'm running on empty here.
-I'm trying!

397
00:25:45,277 --> 00:25:47,767
So how you been?

398
00:25:49,148 --> 00:25:51,318
Wow, sea urchin in the foot.
That sounds pretty nasty.

399
00:25:51,784 --> 00:25:52,654
Yeah.

400
00:25:52,951 --> 00:25:54,441
How do you cure something like that?

401
00:25:55,888 --> 00:25:57,058
You pee on it.

402
00:25:58,023 --> 00:26:00,193
-That's disgusting.
-l know!

403
00:26:00,659 --> 00:26:03,649
Hey. How long am I stuck
with this guy?

404
00:26:04,229 --> 00:26:05,869
-Because you know--
-Till he's better.

405
00:26:06,265 --> 00:26:10,305
Well, come back soon and,
please, bring me some clams.

406
00:26:11,036 --> 00:26:12,376
-No.
-I'm running low here.

407
00:26:12,738 --> 00:26:15,078
I can't keep doing this. You've got
to start taking care of yourself.

408
00:26:15,574 --> 00:26:17,034
-Oh, come on.
-Bye.

409
00:26:17,709 --> 00:26:21,659
-Bring me some more clams!
-Okay.

410
00:26:32,091 --> 00:26:34,460
