Stick, stick, stick, sticky.

417
00:26:51,443 --> 00:26:53,613
It's the way I walk. I'm constantly--

418
00:26:54,079 --> 00:26:56,688
-Boom-chicka-chicka--
-What's with the "boom-chicka-boom"?

419
00:26:57,683 --> 00:27:01,023
I can't stand blood.
I can't stand the sight of blood.

420
00:27:01,653 --> 00:27:05,023
I can't stand...
sight of blood. Cody!

421
00:27:06,692 --> 00:27:10,672
-Dude, have you seen my friend Cody?
-No.

422
00:27:11,763 --> 00:27:14,253
Cody? Cody?

423
00:27:17,136 --> 00:27:18,216
He's not under there.

424
00:27:18,871 --> 00:27:21,331
Cody!

425
00:27:23,509 --> 00:27:24,679
How's it going, man?

426
00:27:28,380 --> 00:27:29,670
So l woke up this morning.

427
00:27:30,015 --> 00:27:33,885
I didn't know where I was. It's never
a good place to be when you wake up.

428
00:27:34,586 --> 00:27:36,516
Come on. Get up.

429
00:27:36,955 --> 00:27:38,445
- don't want to.
-Breakfast.

430
00:27:38,824 --> 00:27:41,844
-Wakey, wakey. Come on.
- don't want to.

431
00:27:43,495 --> 00:27:44,725
-How's your foot?
-My foot--

432
00:27:45,063 --> 00:27:48,663
