I don't know what he thinks.

778
00:49:56,560 --> 00:49:58,400
-You haven't.
-I have. I've been a jerk.

779
00:50:00,030 --> 00:50:02,990
-l have.
-Then go not be a jerk.

780
00:50:04,068 --> 00:50:05,618
