782
00:50:17,948 --> 00:50:19,178
Okay.

783
00:51:21,779 --> 00:51:23,299
Z? No.

784
00:51:24,181 --> 00:51:27,931
No, no, no, don't you do it.
Z, don't do it. No.

785
00:51:28,619 --> 00:51:30,259
-No.
-Let's see here.

786
00:51:30,654 --> 00:51:32,294
-l swear...
-It's stronger than I thought.

787
00:51:32,690 --> 00:51:35,620
-...if you break it--
-Should've been broken by now.

788
00:51:36,193 --> 00:51:38,533
Come on! Come on!

789
00:51:42,633 --> 00:51:44,093
Look at that.

790
00:51:45,903 --> 00:51:49,093
That's the best place
in the world to be, in the tube.

791
00:51:49,707 --> 00:51:50,607
Really?

792
00:51:50,908 --> 00:51:54,778
Yeah. Better than winning,
the trophy, all that stuff.

793
00:51:56,146 --> 00:51:59,106
Tube riding
is the ultimate thing in surfing...

794
00:51:59,683 --> 00:52:01,613
...to ride inside the wave
and make it out of it

795
00:52:02,052 --> 00:52:03,452
It's all we want to do every day.

796
00:52:03,821 --> 00:52:06,401
It's almost impossible to describe.

797
00:52:06,924 --> 00:52:08,624
There's nothing ! can compare it to.

798
00:52:09,026 --> 00:52:12,946
It's a feeling that not too many people
will experience...

799
00:52:13,998 --> 00:52:15,458
