828
00:54:16,820 --> 00:54:21,010
Lani? I like her when
she teaches us because--

829
00:54:21,759 --> 00:54:23,279
Smudge! Not another one!

830
00:54:23,660 --> 00:54:25,879
I think he really has to go
to the bathroom right now.

831
00:54:26,830 --> 00:54:28,350
What's next? The board is done.

832
00:54:28,732 --> 00:54:30,402
-The board is done?
-The board is done.

