00:55:38,702 --> 00:55:42,802
I'm starting to see it, man. I think
I know what you're talking about.

855
00:55:44,308 --> 00:55:46,998
That's great. As long as
we're all having fun, right?

856
00:55:47,644 --> 00:55:51,334
Z, wake up. Wake up, Z. Z!

857
00:56:00,457 --> 00:56:02,187
Hey, Z, breakfast!

858
00:56:04,428 --> 00:56:05,627
Not a chance.

859
00:56:06,129 --> 00:56:09,288
-Four, three, two...
