01:01:43,466 --> 01:01:44,806
Leave me out of it.

922
01:01:45,802 --> 01:01:47,202
Leave me out of it.

923
01:02:14,965 --> 01:02:17,155
I messed up.
I'm just--

924
01:02:17,667 --> 01:02:19,417
