01:02:27,811 --> 01:02:29,951
-What do you mean by--?
-Nothing.

928
01:02:30,447 --> 01:02:32,467
Nothing, man. Forget it.

929
01:02:47,330 --> 01:02:49,350
Peaceful. Peaceful.
I'm in peace. I come in peace.

